        "timestamp": "2018-05-16 23:47:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nGuys, see details on the jira - tested the fix on my live AWS 4 node cluster after an hour still seeing average of 1 core per 3 pods instead of 6-7 cores on a single vm in the cluster - may fix readiness issues on that vm - as detailed by Jun and Shishir.",
