        "timestamp": "2018-05-17 12:02:52.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> actually not this simple - I still need to account for a single\n > node deploy and make the replicaCount parameterized (1 for single\n > node), 3 for 3+ nodes, or ideally n for n\n\nYou can have multiple logstash instances running on a single node although the performance of this might not be much better than a single instance. We should look at making logstash a DaemonSet such that it will automatically scale with the number of nodes in the cluster to achieve the n:n ratio you're looking for.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
