        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-05-17 13:02:29.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWe can have post-install option to set the replica-set until I figure out how to scale based on # of hosts - without the fix one of the hosts is saturated - with the fix the 6core load is distributed",
        "patchset_number": 1
